	<article class="post-635150 post type-post status-publish hentry category-food-beverage category-hedge-funds tag-boards-of-directors tag-mergermarket-group tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-schulte-roth-zabel tag-shareholder-rights-and-activism des-boards-of-directors des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures des-shareholder-rights-and-activism org-mergermarket-group org-schulte-roth-zabel" id="post-635150">
